SQL_STMT_U.val: select :1, sum(q.qrd_value_asset) from qrap_data q , beleggingsinstrument b where q.qrd_opdracht_id= ~2 and q.qrd_instrument = b.be_volgnummer and q.qrd_asset_class between ~3 and ~4 and q.qrd_subasset_class between ~5 and ~6 and b.be_bi_nummer between ~7 and ~8 group by :1 order by :1

select sum(q.qrd_value_asset) from qrap_data q , beleggingsinstrument b where q.qrd_opdracht_id= ~1 and q.qrd_instrument = b.be_volgnummer and q.qrd_asset_class between ~2 and ~3 and q.qrd_subasset_class between ~4 and ~5 and b.be_bi_nummer between ~6 and ~7

select sum(q.qrd_saldo_positie / qrd_koers_vv), sum(q.qrd_duration * q.qrd_saldo_positie / qrd_koers_vv) from qrap_data q , beleggingsinstrument b where q.qrd_opdracht_id= ~1 and q.qrd_instrument = b.be_volgnummer and q.qrd_asset_class between ~2 and ~3 and q.qrd_subasset_class between ~4 and ~5 and b.be_bi_nummer between 200 and 299
